in a landscape = unmatched beauty in my opinion , john cage 's in a landscape is the most beautiful peice for piano of absolute all time . never has there been a classical peice for this instrument that truely got to me personally than this . and never will there ever be . in a landscape goes beyond 'music ' and is an entity in itself that speaks on many levels . it 's so simple and yet is so powerful . this is a must for any music lover or/and a person who would like to get to know the many works of john cage